'''Reena's Interstellar Shipping''' was a small, independent shipping company founded by [[Trinn Reena]].

Among other things it provided technology and [[Weapon/Legends|weapons]] to the isolated [[Chekkoo Province]] of [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]].

